*Altered Hours*: An insomniac's black market sleep aid sends his mind one day into the future where he is suspected of abducting a girl he has not met yet.
2016. Stars: Ryan Munzert, Briana Pozner, Rick Montgomery Jr.

*Lake Artifact*: Â Five friends pick up a drifter on their way to a cabin in Upstate New York for a three day weekend. Upon arrival they discover a picture of themselves posing at the cabin, which they've never been to; Time and space begin to function without rhyme or reason, slowly turning them against each other.
2019.  Stars: Thomas Brazzle, Catharine Daddario, Anna Shields
